<h1>Kanjirappally</h1>\
\
<h2>About</h2>\
<p>Kanjirappally is a beautiful place with natural scenery and a peaceful environment. 
Kanjirappally has the highest number of rainy days in Kerala. It receives the highest amount of summer rains, winter rains and northeast monsoons (Thulaam Mazha) in Kerala, making it one of the very few places in the country with equatorial rainforest type climate, with no distinct dry season. 
Kanjirappally, a scenic town in Kottayam district known as the gateway to the high ranges, offers nature, wildlife, and historical sites. 
</p>\
